<h1 id="advocating-for-accountability-attributing-blame">Advocating for Accountability, Attributing Blame</h1>

<p>As of 2017 (<em>2020 update does not include this information</em>), only 14 officers (3%) had been charged for a killing.  Regardless of whether an officer is charged with a crime, the departments involved are directly responsible for the deaths of these 634 individuals.</p>

